Plans are afoot for the marriage of President Muhammadu Buhari's only son Yusuf to Zarah Ado Bayero, the daughter of the Kano State Emir of Bichi. According to reports, the two met in the UK while doing their undergraduate studies. Negotiations were undertaken by various government officials at the Kano palace on June 27, 2021. Yusuf Buhari was involved in a near-death motorcycle accident in 2017 and had undergone extensive treatment overseas before returning to Nigeria in 2018.